## How to Run

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install torch torchvision scikit-learn scikit-image pandas numpy \
            matplotlib seaborn Pillow huggingface_hub joblib pyarrow jupyter

# Pre-requisite: generate merged_dataset.parquet
jupyter notebook one_imagenet_dataset.ipynb

# Run main pipeline
jupyter notebook CA2_AML_HOG_RF_CNN_Coding.ipynb
```

**Note:** The notebook auto-downloads the ImageNet label map from HuggingFace Hub on first run. Subsequent runs use the cached `imagenet-1k-id2label.json`.

